abstract: Soo-Jin Yang takes third-round lead at LPGA Hana Bank Championship in South Korea; other golf results noted.
snippet: Soo-Jin Yang of South Korea matched the course record with a seven-under-par 65 to take a one-stroke lead in the L.P.G.A. Hana Bank Championship in Incheon, South Korea.
lead_paragraph: Soo-Jin Yang of South Korea matched the course record with a seven-under-par 65 to take a one-stroke lead in the L.P.G.A. Hana Bank Championship in Incheon, South Korea.
